You deserve neither and will share the same bloody fate as the tyrannical oppressors! Most of you acted like sloths!! Treating your lockdown as if it was a government sponsored vacation!! Drinking and stuffing your faces all day instead of improving yourself and investigating what really is going on!!! Which side of history will you fall on when this is over? Choose wisely! Soon all will be revealed and the sheep will drown in lakes of blood!! The lions have awoken!!
